{"title":"旅美诗词节选","authors":["沈鹏"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅美诗词节选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望海潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———尼亚加拉大瀑布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖交汇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美、加连壤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛诡谲奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝壁悬崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神工劈削，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横陈百里银屏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠溅迸明星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾浓蔽天日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩虹升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在何方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心忘何岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入元冥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇观亘古砰訇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能源藏无尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地利堪矜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆昔蛮荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开新大陆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难斩棘披荆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任百万雷霆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有六旬豪女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探险犹生。（注1）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太白匡庐不足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应再谱新声。（注2）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注1：有63岁女教师坐在木桶中冲过瀑布顶端并得以生还，是为第一人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注2：李白句：“飞流直下三千尺，疑是银河落九天。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如梦令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———纽约唐人街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远望琉璃黄瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牌匾汉文题写。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔子立铜雕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《礼运·大同》高挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越中西文化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"———衣阿华州访密西西比河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密西西比老人河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸沧桑故事多。（注1）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩荡非同扬子水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华滋应似古尼罗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往来巨舶销金窟，（注2）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远古悲笳击壤歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印第安人遗书迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临观秋雨骤滂沱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注1：密西西比又名老人河。马克·吐温说密西西比河是一本神奇的书，每天都有新事发生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注2：政府规定可在船上设赌场。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}